{"tid":1447863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場全部抗爭者戴上單眼罩！！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:57:52.000Z","uid":302739,"like":539,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"ecd4bc6bb70bce1446ab3be5c30569ce6e2c7274","tid":1447863,"uid":302739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBN3LRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBN3LRE.jpg&h=f93da8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋絕對唔可以放棄冇咗右眼嘅義士，以後機場嘅集會我哋一定要全部戴上黑色單眼罩，目的係</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 話俾全世界嘅遊客知道黑警嘅極不人道仆街行為</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 致敬依位香港有史以來作出最大犧牲嘅前線</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有Mon post 狗你地同我聽著，你哋冇一個係無辜！！！所有黑警必須落地獄！！！</span>"},{"pid":"effdc283e66e76958ee49ce13b0587b8cc67a5e5","tid":1447863,"uid":171395,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場"},{"pid":"56b19b9d8e4e7d4267795f12a8f0862531723aae","tid":1447863,"uid":15696,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0bssUp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0bssUp.png&h=90693c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxZmxjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxZmxjw.png&h=1d33d451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g1fEi4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg1fEi4i.png&h=ea27d434&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4695c931025e00e42120393fca8bdbc9e1442fcb","tid":1447863,"uid":33543,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%