rt730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=b0aad062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"75db512bf5d87f680591a691a1547f7f06f82148","tid":1447863,"uid":70487,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"藍絲冚家剷，五毛落地獄"},{"pid":"3c68dade40825816ac2e4d88441ba164ce0c8d70","tid":1447863,"uid":302739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96640bc947d1d603d013281ca3afe185a20e2dc0","tid":1447863,"uid":70487,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"75db512bf5d87f680591a691a1547f7f06f82148","tid":1447863,"uid":70487,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"藍絲冚家剷，五毛落地獄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">知法犯法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">下流賤格</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一味靠嚇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">污糟邋遢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">淪為垃圾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">吞槍自殺</span></div></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/lihkg.gif\"